{"tid":702834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老卡門，真係屌你老母","createTime":"2018-06-15T08:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T17:59:30.000Z","uid":167468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35d1f252140517475c1a096b84dc5ca5bc400b50","tid":702834,"uid":167468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩搭輕鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個廢老推撚著惠康間入推車入唔切<br />\n我心入面當然係笑尻佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為 關咗門之後 就開車喇<br />\n點撚估到個廢老聰明到 拎架車一撚野就撞落對門到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一撞就係幾十下 咁個司機就諗住開返門比佢入<br />\n屌佢老母唔撚入嚟，你企係個門中間到做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n磨撚左我十幾廿分鐘<br />\n我屌你老母浪尻費我時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/164630_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F164630_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e2d7ccec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d1f1156e2798c45d8947d546825641a0758630a","tid":702834,"uid":167468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1dfbbf31ff0e467610449063b1073d84d6163a","tid":702834,"uid":165258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"廢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41eed89f882dae503c5e55a4fedd5d84f7914a4f","tid":702834,"uid":53105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:29:48.000Z","msg":"卡到陰"},{"pid":"e630fa2c8beaac6206352a28d89e9a5d0aa76e34","tid":702834,"uid":167468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"推撚死班廢老"},{"pid":"f1992209b4e6c33f11c29d7cf0e029681e14d75a","tid":702834,"uid":167468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說岩岩搭輕鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個廢老推撚著惠康<span style=\"color: red;\">架手</span>推車入唔切<br />\n我心入面當然係笑尻佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為 關咗門之後 就開車喇<br />\n點撚估到個廢老聰明到 拎架車一撚野就撞落對門到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一撞就係幾十下 咁個司機就諗住開返門比佢入<br />\n屌佢老母唔撚入嚟，你企係個門中間到做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n磨撚左我十幾廿分鐘<br />\n我屌你老母浪尻費我時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/164630_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F164630_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e2d7ccec&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8a0b860211f5a6c5e545e906328deff914e99b54","tid":702834,"uid":167468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:33:03.000Z","msg":"推呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9beb27bc2b499b529929fc60262012f8b2af15","tid":702834,"uid":167468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T17:51:39.000Z","msg":"死廢老，過左日都覺得好撚On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d0051c1c00ead27671a051084b33fb5cd9cde7","tid":702834,"uid":167468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/no